      <title>证监会发布公募基金交易费用管理规定，每年可节约成本200亿元 --知识铺</title>
      <link>https://index.zshipu.com/stock001/post/20240420/%E8%AF%81%E7%9B%91%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%9F%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E5%8F%AF%E8%8A%82%E7%BA%A6%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC200%E4%BA%BF%E5%85%83--%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E9%93%BA/</link>
